{"tid":408042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭定康：何君堯「殺無赦」令人震驚　如在英國發生早被判刑","createTime":"2017-09-21T02:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-06T00:16:45.000Z","uid":134071,"like":163,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f0bed8938d0372274ab89fdaed1a11d987581472","tid":408042,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T02:07:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://www.post852.com/229840/%e5%bd%ad%e5%ae%9a%e5%ba%b7%ef%bc%9a%e4%bd%95%e5%90%9b%e5%a0%af%e3%80%8c%e6%ae%ba%e7%84%a1%e8%b5%a6%e3%80%8d%e4%bb%a4%e4%ba%ba%e9%9c%87%e9%a9%9a%e3%80%80%e5%a6%82%e5%9c%a8%e8%8b%b1%e5%9c%8b%e7%99%bc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F229840%2F%25e5%25bd%25ad%25e5%25ae%259a%25e5%25ba%25b7%25ef%25bc%259a%25e4%25bd%2595%25e5%2590%259b%25e5%25a0%25af%25e3%2580%258c%25e6%25ae%25ba%25e7%2584%25a1%25e8%25b5%25a6%25e3%2580%258d%25e4%25bb%25a4%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e9%259c%2587%25e9%25a9%259a%25e3%2580%2580%25e5%25a6%2582%25e5%259c%25a8%25e8%258b%25b1%25e5%259c%258b%25e7%2599%25bc%2F&d=W%2BDrk0pFq8X8upnLo%2Bi4jI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=54725e63\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.post852.com/229840/%e5%bd%ad%e5%ae%9a%e5%ba%b7%ef%bc%9a%e4%bd%95%e5%90%9b%e5%a0%af%e3%80%8c%e6%ae%ba%e7%84%a1%e8%b5%a6%e3%80%8d%e4%bb%a4%e4%ba%ba%e9%9c%87%e9%a9%9a%e3%80%80%e5%a6%82%e5%9c%a8%e8%8b%b1%e5%9c%8b%e7%99%bc/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n2017-9-20 18:22<br />\n字體： A A A<br />\n<br />\n末任港督彭定康近日來港，他今日表示立法會議員何君堯提出的港獨者「殺無赦」言論令人震驚。他同意行政長官林鄭月娥所指，認為這並非文明社會討論問題的方法。如果這種說法令人聯想起文化大革命，將會受全部香港人譴責。<br />\n<br />\n他接受《蘋果日報》訪問時亦表示，自己有時亦會對一些議題有強烈意見，但如果自己前往海德公園讀出想殺死的政治人物名單的話，定會因違反仇恨罪行（hate crime）而被起訴。他亦指在他管治香港期間，從未有人在演說期間表示要殺死和自己意見相左的人；當時香港雖然面對主權移交問題，但從未試過有幾千人上街示威。"},{"pid":"97e3827bb7ceab6f610fd5fa8129031e62e3c5eb","tid":408042,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T02:18:06.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"381ed9d59042cb912f2ae510b6bcacfa33000892","tid":408042,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"